{"tid":647472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳綺莉自嘲身無分文 寸Andi淨係識攞錢","createTime":"2018-04-30T00:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T04:26:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"215f09486452d2d2e296064ec64be7f5082dd2b8","tid":647472,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"吳綺莉女兒吳卓林在加拿大拍片尋父，聲稱與女友Andi三餐不繼兼瞓橋底，成為全城熱話。連日閉關的吳綺莉昨午一時許臉容憔悴離開大坑住所，駕車到北角買豆腐及滷水鵝。問到卓林公開認成龍做父親等問題，她對「成龍」二字全充耳不聞！<br />\n<br />\n吳綺莉接受本報電話訪問時，對於好友郭秀雲爆料指Andi的母親曾提出索取數萬元照顧卓林，她坦言Andi動作多多，目的是向她索取金錢！並自嘲：「我身無分文，都要努力工作嚟維持生活，我咩都唔想理，希望佢好好睇住我個女嘅健康，呢樣嘢最重要。」對於卓林想出自傳，吳綺莉表示去年曾聽聞，但認為女兒年紀還小，沒甚麼經歷可寫，覺得只有對社會有貢獻的成功人士才可出自傳，更指是Andi的主意：「唔該嗰位三十幾歲嘅老師，好好哋搵工，唔好成日將我個女放上神枱供奉，個女梗係乜都聽佢講！其實卓林以前好乖，自從識咗佢之後就變晒！」<br />\n<br />\n被朋友鬧垃圾<br />\n另外，卓林拍片前一天，Andi在社交網以英文發長文，指自己作為教師，見到很多家長不懂教仔，只懂說教，及只想子女去完成他們的夢想等，怎料她的朋友幾乎一面倒爆粗狂罵，以「垃圾」形容她，其朋友留言：「咪做垃圾！快搵嘢做！個個都知你想喺成龍個女身上攞啲乜！」、「你成三十歲人，點解唔搵工畀卓林有瓦遮頭？你殘廢定心理有問題？」、「老師！唔好再叫卓林去乞錢！」、「你愛卓林，應該叫佢返阿媽屋企！」對於Andi的發文及朋友留言，吳綺莉不作回應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CqdcUN1ZlONSOReml4TnjA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/755f6846c73a35f52c7614501b718c22\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCqdcUN1ZlONSOReml4TnjA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F755f6846c73a35f52c7614501b718c22&h=f29703f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E5%90%B3%E7%B6%BA%E8%8E%89%E8%87%AA%E5%98%B2%E8%BA%AB%E7%84%A1%E5%88%86%E6%96%87-%E5%AF%B8andi%E6%B7%A8%E4%BF%82%E8%AD%98%E6%94%9E%E9%8C%A2-214500495.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E7%25B6%25BA%25E8%258E%2589%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%2598%25B2%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%25AF%25B8andi%25E6%25B7%25A8%25E4%25BF%2582%25E8%25AD%2598%25E6%2594%259E%25E9%258C%25A2-214500495.html&d=iasvbpCkUkVJl2lTLqQ2pE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=db0c186c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E5%90%B3%E7%B6%BA%E8%8E%89%E8%87%AA%E5%98%B2%E8%BA%AB%E7%84%A1%E5%88%86%E6%96%87-%E5%AF%B8andi%E6%B7%A8%E4%BF%82%E8%AD%98%E6%94%9E%E9%8C%A2-214500495.html</a>"},{"pid":"35c6cdca77948de616356323831a920db1c2abe1","tid":647472,"uid":131259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:04:29.000Z","msg":"佢條褲係design黎定污糟左"},{"pid":"1936929fcd7ae293bc60888fb5c2473e27496e88","tid":647472,"uid":14497,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"35c6cdca77948de616356323831a920db1c2abe1","tid":647472,"uid":131259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:04:29.000Z","msg":"佢條褲係design黎定污糟左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:25:37.000Z","msg":"精黎"},{"pid":"13d55beaaeaa62dce1d5196391242fb636126f80","tid":647472,"uid":6548,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:46:17.000Z","msg":"唔撚想知 死左先報啦"},{"pid":"05293921feba846db13928f0761fe83310c6ce30","tid":647472,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:48:00.000Z","msg":"比得成x屌既人都唔係善男信女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab251ee616483eed4b1c22c63cc0d9f68f166f7","tid":647472,"uid":156363,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"當初吳綺莉又味係想搵成龍錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢D叫報應啊。"},{"pid":"6e38da417abbb6060e391a742b6dfdf6a6d1dba7","tid":647472,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cab251ee616483eed4b1c22c63cc0d9f68f166f7","tid":647472,"uid":156363,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"當初吳綺莉又味係想搵成龍錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢D叫報應啊。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:00:13.000Z","msg":"呢場戲要做到成龍死果日先會完"},{"p